- gist file export
  - Option to save, or open from gist.
  - Menu bar 'load from'
- github repo integration
  - .barista file with json configuration describing components
  - ex. md-input maps to type fillable.
- Save elements to a database.
- live file preview
  - On any page property change or interaction, ipc call publish.
  - On success refresh the file preview view.
    - Notify user
  - On error, make no changes
